quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  47,1,"ЖЃen yedduЙ“e Allah Й“e sakkii yimЙ“e Й“en e diina Makko kan, Allah bonnii fii golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en."
  47,2,"ЖЃen gomЙ—imЙ“e Allah, Й“e golli golle moЖґЖґe, Й“e gomЙ—ini ko Allah jippini kon e NulaaЙ—o Makko on Muhammadu (yo o his) - on goonga immorЙ—o e Joomi maЙ“Й“e - O yawtanii Й“e bonЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in, O moЖґЖґinii kadi fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e on aduna e laakara."
  47,3,"Ko waЙ—i si Й—in feddeeji Й—iЙ—i yoЙ“itiraa non, ko ko tawi kon yedduЙ“e Allah Й“en jokkii meere nden, gomЙ—imЙ“e Allah e NulaaЙ—o mun on kan jokki goonga kan immorde e Jommi maЙ“Й“e. Fedde kala yoЙ“iraa ko haandi kon. Awa ko wano Allah Й“annginiri non Г±aawoore Й—in feddeeji Й—iЙ—i : gomЙ—imЙ“e e heeferЙ“e, woni ko O piyiranta yimЙ“e Й“en, mise maЙ“Й“e Й—en. O humindira huunde kala e nanndo mun."
  47,4,"Onon muumini'en, si on hawrii e yedduЙ“e Й“en ka hare, ko soppugol daaЙ—e maЙ“Й“e Й—en, jokkiron non haa Й—uЙ—Й—inon warugol Й“e. Si Й—um waЙ—ii, ko haЙ“Й“ugol koyЙ—e dahaaЙ“e Й“en. Ko onon anndi si on accitiray Й“e nii tun, maa si Й“e yoЙ“ay soktiigu ngun. Fow e mun, jokkee haЙ“ugol Й“e ngol, haa hare nden Й“uuЙ“ira silmugol Й“e ngol maa haldigal mon e maЙ“Й“e. Ko jantaa koo, ko Й—um woni Г±aawoore Allah nden, si Allah muuyuno non, O wallirayno gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en e dow heeferЙ“e Й“en, ko aldaa e hare, ko woni tun, O sar'inir jihaadi, fii jarribagol yoga mon e dow yoga: O ndaarndoo haЙ“ooЙ“e Й“en ka muumini'en e Й“e haЙ“ataa Й“en, O ndaarndora gomЙ—inЙ—o on kadi keefeero on; si gomЙ—inЙ—o on waraama, o naata Aljanna, si ko kanko keefeero on, on naata Yiite. Kala non waraaЙ“e fii Allah Й“en, pellet, Allah yeebataa golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en."
  47,5,"Arma O fewna Й“e goonga, e nguurndam maЙ“Й“e aduna, O moЖґЖґina fiyaaku maЙ“Й“e on."
  47,6,"Г‘alnde Darngal, O naadoyay Й“e Aljanna, mo O Й“annginannoo Й“e fii mun."
  47,7,"Ko onon yo gomЙ—imЙ“e Allah,gollirЙ“e ko O sar'ini,si on wallirii Allah, wallugol diina e Annabaajo Makko on haЙ“a heeferЙ“e Й“en,O wallitoray on foolugol Й“e,O tabintina teppe mon Й—en ka haЙ“idugol e maЙ“Й“e."
  47,8,"YedduЙ“e Й“en Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, hayrere e halakuyee woodanii Й“e, Allah bonnii kadi fii golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en."
  47,9,"Ko waЙ—i si on halakuyee yani e maЙ“Й“e, ko tawde Й“e aГ±ii Alqur'aana nde Allah jippini nden e NulaaЙ—o Makko on, fii hinde nodda e bajjinЙ—ingol Mo. Allah bonni fii golle maЙ“Й“e Й—en, Й“e wonti hayruЙ“e aduna e laakara."
  47,10,"E Й“ee fennooЙ“e yiilaaki e leydi ndin, Й“e teskoo ko honno battane Й“eya fennunooЙ“e ado maЙ“Й“e wa'unoo? ЖЉum wonuno ko kaani. Tawde Allah muncituno cuuЙ—i maЙ“Й“e Й—in e hoore maЙ“Й“e, Й“e halkodii e Й“iЙ—Й“e e jawle maЙ“Й“e. Awae hino woodani yedduЙ“e kala jamaanu e nokku."
  47,11,"Ko waЙ—i sabu ndin njoЙ“di haalaandi e Й—in feddeeji Й—iЙ—i, ko tawde ko Allah woni walloowo gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en; hara non yedduЙ“e Й“en, ballo woo alanaa Й“e."